OL,3,CToll charges increase by 20% on the
OL,4,CMersey Gateway and Silver Jubilee
OL,5,Cbridges
OL,7,FDrivers using the toll bridges to
OL,8,Fcross the River Mersey in Halton are
OL,9,Ffacing an increase in travel costs,
OL,10,Fafter a 20% increase in charges.
OL,12,FThe increase is the first of its kind
OL,13,Fin seven years, with car drivers being
OL,14,Fcharged up to #2.40 per crossing.
OL,16,FPenalty Charge Notice (PCN) rates will
OL,17,Falso increase from #40 to #50, but
OL,18,Fanyone who pays within 14 days will be
OL,19,Feligible for a discounted PCN rate of
OL,20,F#25.
