OL,4,CMersey Gateway and Silver Jubilee
OL,5,Cbridges
OL,7,FIn a new scheme, unregistered
OL,8,Fcustomers who receive a PCN for the
OL,9,Ffirst time can choose to use the fine
OL,10,Fto open an account with 'Merseyflow'
OL,11,Fand have their PCN cancelled.
OL,13,FThe Mersey Gateway Crossings Board say
OL,14,Fany future changes will be considered
OL,15,Fevery three years unless there are
OL,16,Fexceptional circumstances.
OL,18,FFor those signing up to a Local User
OL,19,FDiscount Scheme (LUDS), the cost of
OL,20,Fannual plan is increasing by 20% to
OL,21,F#12 per year.
