OL,7,FAlthough there will be a discount to
OL,8,F#10 for eligible Halton residents who
OL,9,Frenew via auto renewal and set up auto
OL,10,Fpayment.
OL,12,FCllr Stef Nelson, Halton Borough
OL,13,FCouncil's portfolio holder for
OL,14,FEnvironment and Urban Renewal, said:
OL,15,F"This will be the first time that toll
OL,16,Fcharges on the bridges have increased
OL,17,Fsince the Mersey Gateway Bridge first
OL,18,Fopened back in 2017.
