OL,7,FMike Bennett, Managing Director of the
OL,8,FMersey Gateway Crossings Board, said:
OL,9,F"Customers don't need to do anything
OL,10,Fin advance as merseyflow's systems
OL,11,Fwill have the new costs built in for
OL,12,Fjourneys made from 1 April, but we
OL,13,Fwant to ensure that people are aware
OL,14,Fof the changes to toll charges and
OL,15,Fother scheme details that have been
OL,16,Fintroduced."
OL,18,FEmails or letters have been sent to
OL,19,Fall vehicle owners registered with
OL,20,Ftoll operator merseyflow to inform
